Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.25,0:00:03.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Biscotti had a brief moment of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.56,0:00:07.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our princess should have been enjoying peaceful days,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but war was suddenly declared!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.11,0:00:13.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a notice of a grand war \Nwagering each country's treasured swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.97,0:00:17.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our princess, Sir Hero, and the knights prepare.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our battle has begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:11.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To Becky: How are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:15.21,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur6\fad(800,505)\pos(139,353)}  「The Day of War」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I haven't contacted you in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.94,0:02:14.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.94,0:02:19.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be participating in a competition starting today and I'll win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:21.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Send.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Today is the great \Nwar between Biscotti and Galette.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Just be careful, and don't get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.70,0:02:33.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:49.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here because I've been\Nsummoned as a hero of Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:53.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the princess who summoned me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and for the sake of this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:02.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:10.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight with the hope that everyone who participates will be able to keep smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.04,0:03:24.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for gathering here so early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:34.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is the day of a great war with Galette.\NDid all of you have a good rest last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:41.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did all of you have a good breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:49.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The normal participants will be divided into groups according to the Knights Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:55.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The battlefield this time will be along\Nthe border between the two countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:02.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our headquarters is located here in the Fortress of Sreize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:08.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, this place will be protected by the \NKnights Army garrison and the support team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:16.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The main force will march along the\Nvalley's sports zone from Chapel Hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, the second force{Force No.2} will go through several kinds of challenges at the fastest speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:25.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right up to Galette's headquarters, the Fortress of Grana.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it'll be a battle of expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:31.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be advancing at a rapid pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:37.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who are not used to war, those who can't catch up, or those who have a sense of discomfort in any form,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:41.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please get in touch with the rescue team immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:48.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's all get into groups!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.87,0:04:51.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And... let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:58.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.47,0:05:00.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same to you too, Senators.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep an eye on this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, you be careful too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:08.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:14.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While I'm away, please help me follow up on\Nsearching for ways to send Sir Hero back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:17.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Just leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:19.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We swear it on the pride of our research team! {there was a name for this research team iinm in previous episode that we did.... look it up if you're free}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time. Please get prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's finally time, Rico!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:34.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you prepared the strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there won't be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is Biscotti's territory, the front of Frianno Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:47.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, the soldiers have begun their march to meet the great war with Galette!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:50.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the number of soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:53.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The participation for Biscotti has reached 20,000 people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:56.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the biggest group over the past few years!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:06:01.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With Laurent Martinozzi, the Leader of Knights Army as captain, the entire army follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:05.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Franboise of Galette, how are things proceeding on your side?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:09.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! We're here in Galette's territory at the front of the Fortress of Wanlet! {check name of fortress from previous episode}{and re-time this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:14.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Galette Army has managed to gather some 23,000 soldiers as well! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.74,0:06:18.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Prince Gaul's army will also participate!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:24.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Looks like everyone will arrive at the battlefield slightly before noon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:29.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that! Next up, Galette's broadcaster, Franboise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:34.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Biscotti's broadcaster, Houshi, will be reporting to you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:42.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noir, Jaune, apparently there will be an unprotected power zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:48.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it thoroughly, and we'll only fight\Nwhere it's safe. There won't be a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:52.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but didn't you hear that ghosts come out at the Fortress of Grana?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:57.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this! I'm only afraid of ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:00.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all of you fools?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:06.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you cut it down the moment it appears, that's good enough, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:09.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'll be done!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The general is so reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.40,0:07:15.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's put ghosts and phantoms aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.16,0:07:20.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is that, where the protection level is weak,\Nthere is a high possibility of demons appearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Demons?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's neither human nor beast
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:30.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but a sinister species that feeds on Flonyard energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:33.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a monster that brings disaster and curses over everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's really scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:38.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noir, horror stories are forbidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:42.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's simply absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:51.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it said that the monster, or whatever it is, was sealed in the depths of the earth hundreds of years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:56.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's reported that way by the theologian and observation teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:00.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there have been eyewitness accounts of demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.04,0:08:06.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've also heard that there are hunters \Nwho specialize in demon extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:12.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hunters remain in darkness, \Nsearching for demons under the moonlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:18.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ridiculous. That's just unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:23.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have been reading too many stories about monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.07,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only hearsay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:27.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.81,0:08:31.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,General, please don't make our Noir upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If she gets upset, it'll take forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I care! Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:44.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I didn't manage to figure out my sister's goals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess and Sink, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:54.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Millhiore and that Sir Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.81,0:08:57.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It seems like they'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:05.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that Millhi might be in danger by reading the stars about half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.41,0:09:07.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:10.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you were worried about the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:15.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was three months ago that her death had been confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:22.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, I knew that the more I tried to \Nrelay the danger to Millhi or the people of Biscotti,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the worse the prediction would become!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:29.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the hero arrived, and everything just appeared as clear as crystal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:37.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Death wasn't to be upon Millhiore but upon the owners of Excellead and Palladion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:43.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that foretelling the future by reading the stars looks suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.62,0:09:49.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving our army based on these claims isn't very smart, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:52.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I honestly believe that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen too clearly over these few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.83,0:10:00.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel very uneasy after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:06.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfectly normal to feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:09.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have informed us, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't run the country by depending on star reading,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:17.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I believe in that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.83,0:10:22.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but the death of Millhiore and that hero would bring unrest and sadness to both countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:27.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hence, I've decided to quit being leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:29.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:32.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only be borrowing the Granveil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of a way myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:40.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can take their Holy Swords away \Nfrom them, it's possible I can avert their deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:46.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But what's gonna happen to the people of Galette if you resign as leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That won't be a problem, will it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:51.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Galette was supposed to be Gaul's, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:55.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was only stepping in before he entered adulthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:02.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though he still isn't very mature, at least he already possesses the ability to save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:06.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he's responsible and \Ncares for the people around him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:09.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he can be a great general.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:14.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree that Prince Gaul has the ability to rule as well as a good character, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:18.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...this has nothing to do with your resignation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:25.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo! Please don't go into ignore mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When this happens, her Excellency is never able to hear anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:32.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo, I'm talking here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:39.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, how about we do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.55,0:11:42.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have a great war that would draw a lot of attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As for the reward, both parties would need to take out their Holy Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.55,0:11:50.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers will definitely be up for it in order to avenge their continuous losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:54.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good chance to initiate a new war.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:57.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as long as we win the war,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:01.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we can hide Biscotti's Holy Swords\Nsomewhere no one can reach or find.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.18,0:12:06.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, we're only doing that to prevent them from being stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with her Excellency's star reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:14.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only offering this suggestion for \Nthe sake of both Galette and Biscotti.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:17.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, your Excellency?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.19,0:12:27.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The march has gone smoothly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:32.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Millhiore's reporters have also been seen quietly moving forward under the protection of the Knights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:36.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess's precious Haran also seems to be in high spirits!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:37.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:42.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess is waving to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:43.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:51.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is against the morality of war by raiding like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.92,0:12:56.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've been the only one to bear the consequences of cowardice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.93,0:13:00.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please say no such thing. Allow us to contribute any little effort we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:05.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We of the Guards Regiment will follow you no matter what, Sister Biore. {i think the "sister" here is just calling an elder person.. like.. what you call someone you respect.}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:06.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:14.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. The first mission today is to \Nsneak in and steal that precious something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:18.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us from the Guards Regiment \Nwill sneak into Biscotti's base camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:23.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll steal the Holy Sword, Excellead, from Princess Millhiore's hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:34.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero and Eclair are on the same team again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:40.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Although it wasn't what I intended, I have to take care of the dumb hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:46.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero, you need to get along with your teammate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:50.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you telling me that? Eclair's the one who's always being mean to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.96,0:13:54.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. That's because you're always doing something stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:13:55.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Something stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard when Sir Hero and Eclair met for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,he touched her breast and looked at her naked body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh gosh! That's interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:07.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:09.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki, how did you know about that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:12.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rico showed me the video of that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:18.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a ton of guts, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was just an unlucky accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you kicking me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:29.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like those two won't have any problem coordinating.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:30.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The only things to worry about now are the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:36.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They shouldn't be an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.01,0:14:40.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sunny day. The wind of protection fills the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:46.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Konoha says that she doesn't feel anything suspicious, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:54.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! It's already the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:59.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Biscotti and Galette are at Chapel Hill after their lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:02.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are waiting for the signal to begin the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:08.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. When the signal to begin appears, we'll use the shortest route to move to the opposite side.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:08.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:13.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as it begins, everyone will be \Nfighting to occupy the bridges and fields.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No one should notice us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:16.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:22.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Artillery Team, it's okay if you don't attack, but make sure you protect Chief Elmar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please follow her closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.98,0:15:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:27.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep everyone waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.95,0:15:29.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle signal will appear shortly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:36.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chapel Hill's live commentary will be brought to you by Biscotti's international broadcaster, Eretasa,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.69,0:15:40.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and Galette's international broadcaster, Jean Cazoni.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:43.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, the countdown is starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:47.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Live audiences, and audiences who are watching the live telecast,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,please join in the countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:52.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,five,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:53.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,four,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:55.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,three,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:56.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,two,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:58.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.23,0:16:05.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Galette Army, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's race forward, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.74,0:16:16.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's our prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys, surround them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Th-This is not what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.65,0:16:27.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:30.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire your arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gale...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:41.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Double Cross!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.66,0:16:51.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Die, Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.48,0:16:53.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:58.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukikaze Style Attack, Flower Storm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:10.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's taboo to be careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:19.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you stop us, there won't be any good points!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wanna turn into a pet ball now, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:28.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that, Ear Drooping Doggie Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not important.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:33.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just need to beat up the hero and get the Holy Sword, Palladion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to get a great reward from her Excellency, Princess Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:44.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you know, you're the one who's getting in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You lone rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you give us some service?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:59.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that dumb hero, I was indeed bare naked before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:05.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I, Eclair Martinozzi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will never, ever,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.82,0:18:18.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,repeat that embarrassment again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eclair!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:31.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad. I... No, the Palladion has become their target.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That may be true, but we can't change our strategy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:42.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a precaution, you better not use the Palladion as a weapon for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That's why I picked up a weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Let's whack them and move forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:47.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:52.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, both sides have intensified their battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:57.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady d'Arquien, who had left the battlefield for two years, seems to be as capable as she used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:18:59.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's charging forward with her favorite Muratsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:07.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise, Panettone has demonstrated her magnificent skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.45,0:19:12.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the performance of those two, the rescue team is having a tough time doing their jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:17.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then again, the earlier you get \Nbeaten down, the earlier you recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:24.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you get beaten down, so long as you still have the stamina,we would like you to still enjoy the war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:28.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, Percy, at the front lines, how are things getting on over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:33.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Just now Biscotti's second team, the Imperial Guards captain and Sir Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.93,0:19:36.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,together with Chief Rico's team, have cut across the wetlands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.94,0:19:40.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fran, and I'm at the route toward the Fortress of Sreize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.66,0:19:44.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a moment ago, Prince Gaul's team had cut across here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:48.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual of Prince Gaul, attacking the enemy from the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:51.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of a war strategy, perhaps?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:54.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, be alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:00.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, we have information.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.33,0:20:05.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Galette's messenger, there's a \Nsuper urgent message to be delivered to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.71,0:20:12.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, please let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:13.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:28.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, my deepest apology for my impudence,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:32.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but please listen to our wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I'm sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:42.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm not the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please don't move, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:53.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:57.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for tricking you with my impersonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:06.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll bring out some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.49,0:21:10.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will listen to everything you want to say, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:18.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Rico's signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe they actually went and raided the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, it's confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.64,0:21:30.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Leo is hiding something from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:34.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of battle, she's always a person who fights fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:43.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And that Princess Leo has gone this far for the Holy Swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.57,0:21:46.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have her reasons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:51.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I must question her personally!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:56.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As the leader of Biscotti, as the owner of Excellead,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:22:02.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and, more importantly, as Millhiore, who loves Princess Leo more than anything in the world!
