Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.78,0:23:53.34,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.33,0:23:54.08,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're so popular, Hero!
