Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.08,0:23:57.85,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The next episode will be about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.85,0:23:59.22,Next Episode Dialogues,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This is annoying.
